A demo to use platform APIs to sample system metrics (e.g. cpu usage,
uptime, thread count, etc).

It includes two parts: system info and process info.

SystemInfo:
    double GetSystemCPUUsage();
    double GetSystemMemoryTotal();
    double GetSystemMemoryUsed();

ProcessInfo:
    unsigned long long GetProcessUptime();
    double GetProcessCPUUsage();
    double GetProcessMemoryUsed();
    unsigned long GetProcessThreadCount();
